<p>I know, most of the U.S. is now under a blanket of either snow and frozen turf, or rain and the addicted, moto-heads, are craving dirt! This is where the Arizona terrain delivers the goods. Perfect sunny days and mild temps are the norm. Where else can you fly in a few hours, and be ripping it up in the same afternoon? Wickenburg, cowboy capital of the southwest, and now, winter singletrack center of the universe. The riding is perfect for all skill levels. Plan a 2 to 3 day adventure and kick those winter blues.<img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2740" src="https://www.oregonmotorcyclerental.com/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain-200x300.jpg 200w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain-97x146.jpg 97w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain-33x50.jpg 33w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain-50x75.jpg 50w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Terrain.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width:767px) 200px, 200px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2738" src="https://www.oregonmotorcyclerental.com/newsite/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-300x294.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="294" srcset="../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-300x294.jpg 300w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-768x753.jpg 768w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-149x146.jpg 149w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-50x50.jpg 50w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group-77x75.jpg 77w, ../../wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Arizona-Motorcyle-Riders-Group.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width:767px) 300px, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="asyn